f the track is good, he will take some pegging back. 15. FLOWERDALE suffered from a cardiac arrhythmia for the first time as the favourite at Geelong and failed to fire. He has been given the all clear at a recent jump-out, and many horses who suffer an arrhythmia often bounce straight back into form at their next start, so follow your money here. 7. DOLLAR CHASER does not win out of turn, but he is an honest type at this level. He ran on too late when finishing second in this grade last start, and he is an each-way hope again, even from a sticky gate. 11. LOUIS BARTHAS is building nicely with 2 wins on the bounce. Watch for him late and include him in all combos.\",\"runners\":[1,15,7,11],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[15,12,2,11]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,3,4,10]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,14,13,15]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,13,11,14]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,14,15,5]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,15,4,7]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,15,5,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"DailyDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"ven